{"tid":527911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新加坡僅跌至22度　當地人穿長袖大呼寒冷","createTime":"2018-01-13T07:37:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-13T07:52:46.000Z","uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8b09fdb631699f3ce593d20974cb85567f8c7e56","tid":527911,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:37:43.000Z","msg":"踏入冬季，不少地方才開始冷，但對去年全年處於熱辣辣的新加坡，如今氣溫僅下降至22度，市民已表示不能適應，紛紛穿起大衣。<br />\n<br />\n新加坡在2017年平均氣溫高達27.7度，比歷史平均值高0.2度，成為有紀錄以來第二熱的一年，其中最熱一天更達到34.6度，因此不少市民早已習慣炎熱天氣。<br />\n<br />\n不過最近受季候風影響，新加坡最低降至22度，不少市民經已高呼受不了。有電台DJ在社交網站貼出合照，數人一起穿上長袖大衣，有人緊握雙拳示意寒冷。<br />\n<br />\n有網民戲稱天氣轉冷，讓他不用到外國旅行也感受到冬季節日氣氛，亦有人表示希望每日也能變得涼快，甚至希望下雪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180112/s00005/1515721876410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180112%2Fs00005%2F1515721876410&d=pPcT3%2FD7b7JsE1P%2BWuD6bcmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=7d881f02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180112%2Fs00005%2F1515721876410&h=c59a22ee\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180112/s00005/1515721876410</a>"},{"pid":"567a905823eafcbcf2a09f18c57f004f18747131","tid":527911,"uid":49918,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"38cd6adfdd6060a4d32524f57c0d90a25862421c","tid":527911,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:39:30.000Z","msg":"JA GA"},{"pid":"681dccb232baf13068a7f63462338b1d6b280c5b","tid":527911,"uid":64095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"567a905823eafcbcf2a09f18c57f004f18747131","tid":527911,"uid":49918,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:39:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:41:04.000Z","msg":"差5度"},{"pid":"e7eabbe5d2231ad798c5713b1e68e4127dc16341","tid":527911,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:43:12.000Z","msg":"有話李光耀冷氣set 23度？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9c9420679b26a38fa19494e368d66296a624c14","tid":527911,"uid":114692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:51:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d18a4cd17f8ce14ff132b5ed9725e4e16a606e68","tid":527911,"uid":33833,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:52:45.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"c9a47888f90e4466ed79420b7e0b094ab9eb3953","tid":527911,"uid":35921,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T07:52:46.000Z","msg":"試過係果度讀書見過d 囡30幾度都可以著住粗冷冷衫係太陽下行 真係世界級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}